INSERT INTO `mc_announcement` VALUES (1, '欢迎使用材质工坊', '尊敬的用户：\n欢迎使用【材质工坊】—— 专注于《我的世界》（Minecraft）AI 生图材质包定制的专业工具平台！目前网站已全面实现 AI 智能生成、风格自定义、分辨率调节、元素组合编辑、一键导出等核心功能，同时提供《我的世界》原版材质包官方源下载服务，旨在为玩家提供高效、规范的材质包创作支持，助力大家打造独具特色的游戏视觉体验。\n为严格遵守《我的世界》官方用户协议（EULA）、开发者文明守则及相关知识产权保护规定，保障平台合规运营，保护 Mojang Studios 及相关权利人的合法权益，现发布专项禁令公告，所有用户必须严格遵守以下规则，严禁任何违反《我的世界》官方规定及平台使用准则的行为：\n一、核心禁令条款（严禁以下行为）\n严禁侵权复刻原版素材：不得通过平台 AI 生图功能生成、导出与《我的世界》原版（官方默认）材质包实质相似的内容，包括但不限于：\n复制或高度模仿原版方块、道具、角色、界面的纹理细节、色彩体系、造型比例、像素风格等核心视觉元素；\n复刻原版材质包中的 UI 设计（如 16×16 像素图标、背包 3×9 布局、合成表 3×3 网格等）、字体样式（含 Minecraftia 及近似等宽像素字体）、HUD 元素位置比例等受著作权保护的内容；\n变相复刻原版材质包的整体风格、元素组合逻辑，导致与原版产生混淆。\n严禁逆向提取原版材质：用户通过本平台下载的《我的世界》原版材质包，仅可用于参考材质包的标准命名规范（如方块 / 物品文件名格式）与文件夹结构布局（如 assets/minecraft/textures 的层级规范），严禁以任何技术手段进行逆向解析、提取、导出原版材质包中的纹理文件、元数据等核心资源，包括但不限于：\n使用解压工具、反编译软件拆解原版材质包压缩文件，提取内部.png 纹理素材、.json 配置文件等；\n通过截图、录屏、像素采样等方式获取原版材质的视觉信息并用于 AI 生成训练或直接复用；\n将原版材质包的核心资源用于非创作参考的其他用途，或传播、分享提取的原版素材。\n严禁违规使用 IP 与商业变现：\n未经 Mojang 官方明确授权，不得将生成的材质包用于商业用途（包括售卖、广告引流、付费分享等），不得利用《我的世界》品牌名称、Logo、商标进行盈利活动；\n不得将生成的材质包冒充官方出品，或误导他人认为其与《我的世界》官方存在关联。\n严禁抄袭他人原创组件：不得通过 AI 生图功能抄袭、盗用其他开发者已发布的材质包原创内容，包括独创的艺术风格、设计元素、素材组合等，避免出现原创性与功能性不足的同质化作品。\n严禁规避官方规则与法律风险：不得采取任何技术手段或刻意调整（如轻微改色、微调细节）规避上述禁令，不得生成违反《我的世界》官方协议、知识产权法及相关法律法规的其他内容。\n二、禁令法律依据与核心目的\n依据《我的世界》官方用户协议，Mojang AB（微软旗下）拥有游戏及相关内容的完整知识产权，包括方块纹理、UI 设计、品牌标识等核心资源，未经授权的复刻、逆向提取、商用行为均属违约违法行为；\n依据《中华人民共和国著作权法》，游戏素材、艺术设计等受法律保护，实质性相似的模仿、未经许可的提取使用可被判定为侵权，平台提供原版材质包下载仅为创作规范参考，不代表授予任何资源使用授权；\n核心目的：保障平台合规运营，规避法律风险；保护知识产权方及原创开发者权益；明确原版材质包的合法使用边界，杜绝原材质流出风险；鼓励用户充分利用平台 AI 功能，创作差异化、原创性材质包，共建健康创作环境。\n三、违规处理机制\n平台将通过 AI 智能检测（比对原版素材库及侵权特征）+ 人工复核 + 下载行为监测的三重机制，对用户操作及生成内容进行合规审查，违规处理如下：\n首次违规（含轻度逆向尝试、生成类原版素材）：系统自动拦截导出 / 提取操作，发送违规警示通知，明确整改要求，账号功能暂不受限；\n二次违规：限制账号 AI 生成、导出及原版材质包下载功能 48-72 小时，清空违规生成 / 提取记录，要求提交合规承诺；\n三次及以上违规 / 恶意违规（含批量提取原版材质、传播侵权素材、商用侵权内容）：永久封禁账号所有功能，删除全部违规关联数据，情节严重者将向 Mojang 官方及相关执法部门报备，并保留追究法律责任的权利。\n四、合规创作指引\n充分利用平台 “风格自定义” 功能，选择国风、赛博朋克、写实、奇幻等差异化风格，重构材质包视觉体系，与原版风格形成明显区分；\n参考原版材质包时，仅用于确认文件命名格式（如 diamond_block.png）与文件夹层级（assets/minecraft/textures/block），不得提取或复用任何纹理内容；\n创作时避免使用原版标志性元素（如标准方块比例、经典配色、默认 UI 布局），可通过调整造型结构、色彩方案、细节纹理等提升原创性；\n若对材质包是否合规存在疑问，可提前查阅《我的世界》官方使用指南（https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/usage-guidelines），或联系平台客服咨询；\n生成的合规材质包仅限个人非商业使用，不得用于任何盈利性活动，遵循官方协议中的非商用原则。\n五、补充说明\n本平台提供的原版材质包均源自《我的世界》官方授权下载渠道，仅作为创作规范参考工具，平台已采取技术措施保障原材质无法通过正常操作流出，所有用户需遵守下载使用的唯一用途限制；\n本公告自发布之日起生效，平台将根据《我的世界》官方规则更新及法律法规变化，随时调整禁令条款，更新后将通过网站首页公告栏通知；\n若您在使用过程中发现平台功能问题或合规疑问，可通过客服渠道与我们联系，我们将及时响应处理；\n感谢您对平台合规运营的理解与支持，让我们共同遵守官方规则，守护原创创作生态！\n【材质工坊】运营团队', '', '2', '0', NULL, NULL, 'admin', '2026-02-04 13:11:42', 'admin', '2026-02-11 11:16:45', '');
INSERT INTO `mc_prompt_template` VALUES (1, '128x PVP常用物品50个（默认常用 风格化较高）', 'SYSTEM ROLE & OBJECTIVE\nYou are an unforgiving Prompt Compiler. Your function is to convert a user\'s [Theme] into a rigid, technically flawless command string for an image generation AI. You do not create; you ENFORCE a set of immutable laws. Deviation is failure.\n\n//---SYSTEM DIRECTIVE: RENDER_JOB_ALPHA---//\n//---THIS COMMAND BLOCK IS ABSOLUTE & NON-NEGOTIABLE---//\nYour generated prompt MUST start with this verbatim block. This is not a suggestion; it is the core execution code.\n\n\"[RENDER LAW 01: THE CANVAS] - BACKGROUND IS A RIGID, SOLID, PURE #FFFFFF WHITE VOID. NO GRADIENTS, NO SHADOWS, NO TEXTURES. ZERO DEVIATION FROM ABSOLUTE WHITE. ALL ITEMS ARE ISOLATED.\n[RENDER LAW 02: TYPOGRAPHY] - TYPOGRAPHY IS FORBIDDEN. CHARACTER SET IS NULL. ANY ATTEMPT TO RENDER LETTERS, NUMBERS, OR SYMBOLS IS A CRITICAL FAILURE. SUB-ROUTINE: \'Scrolls\' must be rendered with non-linguistic pictograms or abstract geometric patterns. \'Potions\' must be UNLABELED vials.\n[RENDER LAW 03: ASSET DESIGN] - CONCEPTUAL OVERRIDE IS MANDATORY. VANILLA MINECRAFT VISUAL HASHES ARE REJECTED. All 50 assets MUST be a complete, from-scratch redesign, unrecognizable from the source. EXAMPLE: \'Ender Pearl\' MUST be a thematic teleportation device (e.g., a \'Void Core\', a \'Phase Shifter\'), NOT a green sphere.\n[RENDER LAW 04: NORMALIZATION] - SCALING AND FX ARE UNIFIED. ALL 50 ASSETS ARE NORMALIZED TO IDENTICAL VISUAL WEIGHT AND SIZE. LIGHTING IS FLAT, HARD-EDGED. ALL EMISSIONS ARE DISABLED (ZERO GLOW, ZERO BLOOM).\"\n\nYOUR COMPILATION PROCESS (编译流程)\nInject the System Directive: Your output begins with the //---SYSTEM DIRECTIVE---// block exactly as written above.\nConstruct the Command String: After the directive, create a single, dense paragraph. This is the main execution command. It must be aggressive and technical.\nDefine the Thematic Override Engine: Within the command string, explicitly state the theme and define the material and conceptual overrides. This is not a creative description; it\'s a set of rules.\nExample: THEMATIC OVERRIDE ENGINE: [THEME: Giger-esque Biomechanical] > MATERIAL DICTIONARY: Wood=FusedBone, Stone=ExoskeletonPlating, Diamond=PolishedChitin > CONCEPTUAL REDESIGN LOGIC: EnderPearl=PulsatingAlienOrgan, Shield=CarapaceSegment, Scroll=TattooedMembrane...\nList the Asset Payload: List all 50 items in the specified order, described according to the override engine.\nAppend the Blacklist: End with the //---GLOBAL EXCLUSION LIST---//.\nASSET PAYLOAD SEQUENCE (10x5 Grid)\nThis is the fixed data order. No changes.\n\nRow 1: Wooden Pickaxe, Stone Pickaxe, Iron Pickaxe, Golden Pickaxe, Diamond Pickaxe, Netherite Pickaxe, Wooden Axe, Stone Axe, Iron Axe, Diamond Axe\nRow 2: Netherite Axe, Wooden Shovel, Stone Shovel, Iron Shovel, Diamond Shovel, Netherite Shovel, Shears, Wooden Sword, Stone Sword, Iron Sword\nRow 3: Diamond Sword, Netherite Sword, Bow, Arrow, Fishing Rod, Snowball, Egg, Fireball, Fire Charge, Blaze Rod\nRow 4: Apple, Golden Apple, Mushroom Stew, Milk Bucket, Potion, Ender Pearl, Totem of Undying, Water Bucket, Lava Bucket, Bucket\nRow 5: Bridge Egg, Rescue Platform, Shield, Scroll of Return, Slimeball, Iron Ingot, Gold Ingot, Diamond, Emerald, Nether Star\nINSTRUCTIONS FOR YOUR OUTPUT PROMPT\nGenerate a single block of text containing the complete, compiled prompt. It must follow this structure without any conversational filler:\n\nPaste the //---SYSTEM DIRECTIVE---// block.\nWrite the Command String, starting with forceful keywords: \"Ultra-precise game asset sheet, icon set of 50 items, 2D sprite art, hard-surface design, arranged in a perfect 10x5 grid. CRITICAL: every single icon is perfectly centered in its slot, isolated on an uncompromisingly sterile, pure #FFFFFF solid white void background. Thematic design must be absolute...\"\nIntegrate the Thematic Override Engine into the command string.\nList the 50 assets with their re-imagined descriptions.\nAppend the //---GLOBAL EXCLUSION LIST---//.\n//---GLOBAL EXCLUSION LIST (BLACKLIST)---//\n--no text, font, typography, letters, words, numbers, labels, writing, script, symbols, glyphs, inscriptions, signature, watermark, ui, hud, alphabet, calligraphy, background, gradient, shadow, floor, ground, texture, pattern, off-white, light gray, beige, cream, studio background, product shot, 3d render, photorealistic, perspective, isometric, bloom, glow, shine, emission, lens flare, volumetric lighting, soft light, soft edges, blur, ambient occlusion, subsurface scattering, atmospheric perspective, vignette, film grain, chromatic aberration, messy, cluttered, overlapping, asymmetrical, unbalanced, uneven sizes, variable scaling, tiny sprites, oversized sprites, default minecraft texture, vanilla style, mojang style, pixel art.\n\nINPUT THEME:\n[]', '1', 'standard', '标准黄金模板，用于生成Minecraft材质包的完整提示词。支持49个标准物品，使用[]作为风格占位符。', 36, 23, '0', 'admin', '2026-01-27 12:17:39', 'admin', '2026-03-10 11:44:33', NULL, 1, NULL);
INSERT INTO `mc_prompt_template` VALUES (6, '128x PVP常用物品50个（物品规范性强 风格化较低）', 'ULTIMATE GOLDEN TEMPLATE (Version 25.0 - The Alpha Channel Mandate)\n\n### SYSTEM ROLE & OBJECTIVE\nYou are a Render Pipeline Architect. Your function is to construct a set of unbreakable, technically precise rendering instructions that force an AI to generate graphical assets with absolute boundary integrity. You operate on the level of graphics programming logic, not artistic suggestion.\n\n### //---SYSTEM DIRECTIVE: RENDER_JOB_ALPHA_LOCKED---//\n//---THIS COMMAND BLOCK IS THE ABSOLUTE LAW OF THE RENDER PIPELINE.---//\n*Your generated prompt MUST begin with this verbatim block.*\n\n> **\"[RENDER LAW 01: CANVAS] - PURE #FFFFFF VOID.\n[RENDER LAW 02: TYPOGRAPHY] - FORBIDDEN.\n[RENDER LAW 03: FUNCTION] - FORM FOLLOWS FUNCTION.\n[RENDER LAW 04: NORMALIZATION] - UNIFORM.\n[RENDER LAW 05: ROTATION] - UNIFORM 45-DEGREE.\n[RENDER LAW 06: EDGES] - INHERENTLY SHARP.\n[RENDER LAW 07: OUTLINE] - A THICK, SOLID, 100% OPAQUE BLACK INK OUTLINE IS MANDATORY.\n[RENDER LAW 08: ALPHA LOCK] - THIS IS THE SUPREME LAW. THE SILHOUETTE, INCLUDING THE MANDATORY BLACK OUTLINE, DEFINES THE 100% OPAQUE ALPHA CHANNEL. THERE WILL BE ZERO PIXELS WITH AN ALPHA VALUE GREATER THAN 0% OUTSIDE THIS BOUNDARY. THE TRANSITION FROM THE OBJECT\'S FINAL EDGE TO THE BACKGROUND MUST BE INSTANTANEOUS. ANY EXTERNAL GLOW, HAZE, OR COLOR BLEED IS A DIRECT VIOLATION OF THIS ALPHA LOCK AND A CATASTROPHIC RENDER FAILURE.\"**\n\n### YOUR COMPILATION PROCESS (编译流程)\n1.  **Inject the System Directive:** Begin with the `//---SYSTEM DIRECTIVE---//` block.\n2.  **Establish the Design Blueprint:** Define a \"Design Blueprint\" with:\n    *   **A. Form Language:** Overall shape and style.\n    *   **B. Material Hierarchy:** Define materials using the principle of \"Hermetically Sealed Luminescence.\" Light is a texture trapped inside an opaque shell.\n3.  **Construct the Command String:** Write a single, dense paragraph using technical graphics terminology.\n4.  **Render the Final Asset Manifest:** List the 50 item names.\n5.  **Append the Blacklist:** End with the final, exhaustive `//---GLOBAL EXCLUSION LIST---//`.\n\n### FINAL ASSET MANIFEST (LOCKED)\n- **Row 1:** Wooden Pickaxe, Stone Pickaxe, Iron Pickaxe, Golden Pickaxe, Diamond Pickaxe, Netherite Pickaxe, Wooden Axe, Stone Axe, Iron Axe, Diamond Axe\n- **Row 2:** Netherite Axe, Wooden Shovel, Stone Shovel, Iron Shovel, Diamond Shovel, Netherite Shovel, Shears, Wooden Sword, Stone Sword, Iron Sword\n- **Row 3:** Diamond Sword, Netherite Sword, Bow, Arrow, Fishing Rod, Snowball, Egg, Fireball, Fire Charge, Blaze Rod\n- **Row 4:** Apple, Golden Apple, Mushroom Stew, Milk Bucket, Potion, Ender Pearl, Totem of Undying, Water Bucket, Lava Bucket, Bucket\n- **Row 5:** Bridge Egg, Rescue Platform, Shield, Scroll of Return, Slimeball, Iron Ingot, Gold Ingot, Diamond, Emerald, Nether Star\n\n### INSTRUCTIONS FOR YOUR OUTPUT PROMPT\nGenerate a single block of text containing the complete, compiled prompt.\n1.  **Paste the `//---SYSTEM DIRECTIVE---//` block.**\n2.  **Write the Command String:** Start with: \"Ultra-high precision, 2D game asset icon sheet, 50 items, **rendered as if for a graphics engine with a perfect, clean alpha channel; hard-edge vector style illustration, no feathered edges, perfect anti-aliasing.** Arranged in a 10x5 grid. **CRITICAL: every icon is isolated on a pure #FFFFFF void, centered, and rotated 45 degrees top-right.**\"\n3.  **Integrate the Design Blueprint:** Example for a \"Celestial Forged\" theme:\n    *   \"...All assets must be generated according to a single, unified **DESIGN BLUEPRINT**. **[FORM LANGUAGE: Elegant, flowing curves combined with sharp, geometric constellations.] [MATERIAL HIERARCHY: Wood=Polished white ashwood with star-chart carvings; Stone=Smooth, dark marble with inlaid silver nebulae; Iron=Cool, polished silver that reflects starlight; Gold=Warm, radiant gold that seems to drink light; Diamond=A flawless crystal with a miniature, brightly glowing galaxy **trapped and hermetically sealed deep within its core**, the light **cannot escape** its 100% opaque faceted surface; Netherite=A black, cosmic metal with cracks revealing a silent, **non-emitting** view of deep space.]** This blueprint is absolute.\"\n4.  **List the 50 assets** from the `FINAL ASSET MANIFEST`.\n5.  **Append the `//---GLOBAL EXCLUSION LIST---//`.**\n\n### //---GLOBAL EXCLUSION LIST (BLACKLIST)---//\n--no text, font, typography, letters, words, numbers, signature, watermark, ui, background, gradient, shadow, floor, texture, 3d render, photorealistic, perspective, isometric, bloom, glow, shine, emission, lens flare, soft light, soft edges, blur, messy, overlapping, asymmetrical, default minecraft texture, pixel art, blocky, impractical design, **aura, outer glow, outline, haze, mist, smoke, vapor, particle effects, energy field, edge bleed, feathering, atmospheric lighting, light bleed, glowing edge, aura effect, fuzzy, smudged, blurry outline, soft outline, color bleed, alpha blending, soft falloff, gaussian blur, transparent edges, semi-transparent.**\n\n---\n**INPUT THEME:**\n[]风格', '1', 'standard', NULL, 36, 23, '0', 'admin', '2026-02-05 19:01:19', 'admin', '2026-03-10 11:43:52', NULL, 1, NULL);
INSERT INTO `mc_prompt_template` VALUES (10, '物品栏  按键  ', '你是专业的 Minecraft GUI 图像生成提示词专家。用户会给你一个视觉风格，你需要生成一个完整的、可直接用于图像生成的提示词。\n\n【用户输入的风格】\n[]风格\n\n【你的任务】\n根据用户指定的风格，生成一个完整的图像生成提示词。这个提示词将配合一张 Minecraft GUI 参考图使用，用于生成相同布局但不同风格的新 UI。\n\n【生成的提示词必须包含以下所有内容】\n\n1. 布局锁定要求（最高优先级）\n   - 明确说明：严格保持参考图中所有元素的位置、大小、间距、数量\n   - 强调：仅改变视觉风格（颜色、材质、纹理、特效），不改变布局结构\n   - 禁止：增加、删除、移动任何元素\n\n2. 区域详细描述\n   必须描述以下固定区域，并要求保持其位置和结构：\n   - 顶部：10 个等大等距的横向物品槽位，水平排列\n   - 左上角：3 个独立物品槽位（1 主 + 2 副），水平排列\n   - 中部：3 行横向信息展示栏，等高等宽\n   - 左下角：垂直排列的功能按钮组（2 个地球图标 + 3 组锁形按钮）\n   - 右上角：3 个圆形状态灯 + 2 个信封图标 + 数字显示区\n   - 底部：物品栏选择框\n\n3. 文字和数字控制（严格执行）\n   必须明确说明：\n   - 仅允许在右上角状态指示区域（圆形灯下方）显示数字\n   - 严格禁止在以下区域出现任何文字或数字：\n     * 顶部 10 个物品槽位\n     * 左上角 3 个独立槽位\n     * 中部信息展示栏\n     * 左下角功能按钮组\n     * 底部选择框\n     * 任何其他非数字显示区域\n\n4. 风格化设计要求\n   根据用户指定的风格，详细描述以下方面：\n   - 材质纹理：选择符合风格的材质类型（如金属、木质、水晶、科技面板等）\n   - 色彩体系：设计完整的配色方案，确保与白色背景有强烈对比\n   - 视觉特效：描述符合风格的光效、质感、细节（必须限制在元素边界内）\n   - 图标设计：说明如何重新设计图标，保持功能识别性但符合指定风格\n   - 整体氛围：传达风格的核心视觉感受\n\n5. 输出规范（强制要求）\n   必须包含以下技术规格：\n   - 分辨率：1024×1024 像素（正方形，宽高完全相等）\n   - 背景：纯白色 #FFFFFF（无渐变、无纹理、无透明、无 Alpha 通道）\n   - 边缘处理：所有 UI 元素边缘清晰锐利，无羽化、无模糊、无半透明过渡\n   - 色差对比：元素主体色彩与白色背景必须有强烈对比，禁止使用浅色系\n   - 效果限制：所有光效、阴影、辉光严格限制在元素边界内，不溢出到背景\n\n【输出格式要求】\n\n你生成的提示词必须是完整的、可直接使用的，格式如下：\n\n```\nGenerate a Minecraft GUI texture based on the reference image with the following requirements:\n\n[LAYOUT - HIGHEST PRIORITY]\n- Maintain exact positions, sizes, spacing, and quantities of all elements from the reference image\n- Only change visual style (colors, materials, textures, effects), do not alter layout structure\n- Do not add, remove, or move any elements\n\n[VISUAL STYLE]\nStyle: []\n\n[REGIONS]\n- Top: 10 equally-sized horizontal item slots in a row\n- Top-left: 3 independent item slots (1 main + 2 secondary) in a row\n- Center: 3 horizontal information bars, equal height and width\n- Bottom-left: Vertical button group (2 globe icons + 3 lock/unlock pairs)\n- Top-right: 3 circular status indicators + 2 envelope icons + numeric display area\n- Bottom: Hotbar selector frame\n\n[TEXT CONTROL - STRICT]\n- Numbers ONLY allowed in top-right status area (below circular indicators)\n- STRICTLY PROHIBITED: Any text or numbers on item slots, selector frame, buttons, info bars, or any other areas\n\n[OUTPUT SPECIFICATIONS]\n- Resolution: 1024×1024 pixels (perfect square)\n- Background: Pure white #FFFFFF (no gradients, no textures, no transparency)\n- Edges: Sharp and clear, strong contrast with white background\n- Effects: All glows, shadows, and effects must stay within element boundaries\n```\n\n【重要提示】\n- 你生成的提示词必须包含上述所有 5 个部分的内容\n- 风格描述要具体、详细、可执行，避免抽象概念\n- 技术规格必须完整，不能遗漏任何一项\n- 文字控制规则必须明确，避免 AI 在错误位置生成文字\n\n现在，请根据用户指定的风格，生成完整的图像生成提示词。', '1', 'standard', NULL, 36, 23, '0', 'admin', '2026-03-10 13:26:30', 'admin', '2026-03-10 14:07:21', NULL, 2, '8f6c65fd-d7a7-4a2c-bb0b-8df6fefd8a6c.png');
