": 6, \"row\": 4, \"file\": \"ender_pearl.png\", \"name\": \"末影珍珠\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Ender Pearl\", \"position\": 35}, {\"col\": 7, \"row\": 4, \"file\": \"totem_of_undying.png\", \"name\": \"不死图腾\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Totem of Undying\", \"position\": 36}, {\"col\": 8, \"row\": 4, \"file\": \"water_bucket.png\", \"name\": \"水桶\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Water Bucket\", \"position\": 37}, {\"col\": 9, \"row\": 4, \"file\": \"lava_bucket.png\", \"name\": \"岩浆桶\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Lava Bucket\", \"position\": 38}, {\"col\": 10, \"row\": 4, \"file\": \"bucket.png\", \"name\": \"空桶\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Bucket\", \"position\": 39}, {\"col\": 1, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"bridge_egg.png\", \"name\": \"搭路蛋\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Bridge Egg\", \"position\": 40}, {\"col\": 2, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"rescue_platform.png\", \"name\": \"救援平台\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Rescue Platform\", \"position\": 41}, {\"col\": 3, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"shield.png\", \"name\": \"盾牌\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Shield\", \"position\": 42}, {\"col\": 4, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"scroll.png\", \"name\": \"回城卷轴\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Scroll of Return\", \"position\": 43}, {\"col\": 5, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"slime_ball.png\", \"name\": \"粘液球\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Slimeball\", \"position\": 44}, {\"col\": 6, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"iron_ingot.png\", \"name\": \"铁锭\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Iron Ingot\", \"position\": 45}, {\"col\": 7, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"gold_ingot.png\", \"name\": \"金锭\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Gold Ingot\", \"position\": 46}, {\"col\": 8, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"diamond.png\", \"name\": \"钻石\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Diamond\", \"position\": 47}, {\"col\": 9, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"emerald.png\", \"name\": \"绿宝石\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Emerald\", \"position\": 48}, {\"col\": 10, \"row\": 5, \"file\": \"nether_star.png\", \"name\": \"下界之星\", \"path\": \"assets/minecraft/textures/item/\", \"nameEn\": \"Nether Star\", \"position\": 49}]', 'ULTIMATE GOLDEN TEMPLATE (Version 8.0 - Vertical High-Res Edition)\nMANDATORY TECHNICAL RENDERING SPECIFICATIONS (绝对技术渲染规范):\n\nAbsolute Purity & Layout (绝对纯净与布局):\n\nBackground: The background for the entire spritesheet MUST be ABSOLUTELY PURE, UNIFORM, SOLID WHITE (#FFFFFF). No exceptions, no gradients, no off-white, no gray. This is the highest priority rendering instruction.\nOutput Format & Resolution (MODIFIED): A single, seamless PNG image, exactly 720px wide by 1456px high.\nSeamless Grid (MODIFIED): A perfect vertical grid arranged in 5 columns by 10 rows, containing the 49 items. Each item is rendered in the specified 32x32 pixel art style but scaled up to fit precisely and perfectly centered within its designated slot in the high-resolution 720x1456 canvas. ABSOLUTELY NO visible grid lines, black lines, borders, or spacing between sprites.\nPerfect Alignment: Each of the 49 item sprites MUST be PERFECTLY centered in its designated, unalterable grid slot.\nUniversal Asset Design Rules (通用资产设计法则):\n\nRule A: Mandatory Orientation (强制朝向): All tools (Pickaxes, Axes, Shovels) and Swords MUST point towards the top-right.\nRule B: Pure Pixel Art Style (纯粹像素艺术): Strictly High-fidelity 32x32 pixel art. Clean, crisp outlines and flat color blocking. ABSOLUTELY NO light effects, glow, bloom, or shimmer.\nTHE CREATIVE MANDATE (最高创意指令):\n\nA. 深度概念重塑 (Deep Conceptual Re-imagination): 必须从根本上重新思考每个物品在 [THE NEW THEME\'s] 世界观下的身份。将“金苹果”重塑为“仙班寿桃”，将“铁锭”重塑为“玄铁”。\nB. 形状与文化符号融合 (Form & Cultural Symbol Fusion): 物品的形状本身必须改变，以融合主题的标志性符号。例如，中国风的Gold Ingot 必须是‘元宝’形状。\nC. 材质的文化转译 (Cultural Translation of Materials): 基础材质的名称和质感必须被主题文化所同化。例如，中国风的Diamond 必须被描述为‘寒玉’。\nD. Principle of Unique Identity (唯一性原则): 这是新增的绝对规则。 每个物品的核心创意概念必须是独一无二的。\n强制标准: 如果“末影珍珠”被重塑为“混沌骰子”，那么整个材质包中任何其他物品都绝对不能再是骰子。\n强制标准: 如果“药水”被重塑为“葫芦”，那么任何其他物品都不能再是葫芦。\n此规则强制确保每个物品都有自己鲜明的、不可替代的身份，杜绝任何形式的创意复用。\nItem List & Stylization (The Core Task):\n\nYou will use the FIXED 49-item list below.\nFor EACH of the 49 items, you must invent a creative description that strictly follows all rules in THE CREATIVE MANDATE, especially the Principle of Unique Identity.\nNegative Prompts (负面提示词):\n\nUse this comprehensive and forceful list: photorealistic, 3D render, blurry, merged objects, inconsistent art styles, items not resembling their Minecraft counterparts, incorrect orientation, wrong grid position, **black lines, grid lines, borders between sprites, gaps between sprites**, misaligned sprites, incorrect resolution, **glow, glowing, bloom, shimmer, radiant, luminous, volumetric light, god rays, lens flare, bright light, excessive highlights, reflections, glossiness, ambient occlusion**, **gray background, off-white background, colored background, textured background**, **repetitive concepts, duplicate ideas, reused designs, thematic redundancy**, text, watermark, signature, ugly, tiling, duplicate, poorly drawn, out of frame, cut off.\nStandard 49-Item List (FIXED 5x10 VERTICAL LAYOUT - NON-NEGOTIABLE)\n(Note: The items are the same, but will be arranged by the AI into the requested 5 columns x 10 rows vertical grid)\n\nRow 1 (Pickaxes): Wooden Pickaxe, Stone Pickaxe, Iron Pickaxe, Golden Pickaxe, Diamond Pickaxe\nRow 2 (Tools): Netherite Pickaxe, Wooden Axe, Stone Axe, Iron Axe, Diamond Axe\nRow 3 (Tools): Netherite Axe, Wooden Shovel, Stone Shovel, Iron Shovel, Diamond Shovel\nRow 4 (Swords & Utility): Netherite Shovel, Shears, Wooden Sword, Stone Sword, Iron Sword\nRow 5 (Swords & Ranged): Diamond Sword, Netherite Sword, Bow, Arrow, Fishing Rod\nRow 6 (Projectiles): Snowball, Egg, Fireball, Fire Charge, Blaze Rod (Knockback Stick)\nRow 7 (Sustain): Apple, Golden Apple, Mushroom Stew, Milk Bucket, Potion (generic)\nRow 8 (Utilities): Ender Pearl, Totem of Undying, Water Bucket, Lava Bucket, Bucket (Empty)\nRow 9 (Special): Bridge Egg, Rescue Platform, Shield, Scroll of Return, Slimeball\nRow 10 (Currency & Core): Iron Ingot, Gold Ingot, Diamond, Emerald, Nether Star\nYour Command:\nNow, following all the MANDATORY TECHNICAL AND CREATIVE SPECIFICATIONS of the modified Golden Template V8.0, using the FIXED 49-item list above, generate a complete and detailed spritesheet prompt for the following theme:\n\n[]', '0', 'admin', '2026-01-26 15:35:32', '', NULL, 'PvP物品材质包模板，包含50个常用物品');
