Directive: Your output begins with the //---SYSTEM DIRECTIVE---// block exactly as written above.\\nConstruct the Command String: After the directive, create a single, dense paragraph. This is the main execution command. It must be aggre', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}', 0, NULL, '2026-02-28 22:38:35', 13);
