* Overall shape and style.\\n    *   **B. Material Hierarchy:** Define materials using the principle of \\\"Hermetically Sealed Luminescence.\\\" Light is a texture trapped inside an opaque shell.\\n3.  **Construct the Command String:** Writ', '{\"msg\":\"操作成功\",\"code\":200}', 0, NULL, '2026-03-10 11:43:49', 12);
